From (11), we observe that the market inﬂuence power of MVNO m ∈ M is coupled with the bids of other competing MVNOs, however, these bids are their private information. In such a case, one can employ an iterative algorithm that allows the MVNO to know the approximate market inﬂuence power from the information related with the previous iterations. Thus, for the MVNO m ∈ M, its market inﬂuence power at the kth iteration can be deﬁned as

