B. Lower-level Problem
In the lower-level, each MVNO aims at maximizing its valuation by allocating the obtained bandwidth from the InP. The valuation of each MVNO m ∈ M is the sum of the logarithmic function of data rate of its users. Therefore, the valuation of an MVNO m ∈ M can be deﬁned as:

