D. Lower-level Problem with Incomplete Information

In a practical scenario, it is hard for MVNOs to get precise information of the channels (bandwidth) because of the estimation errors, and the wireless channel delay. To address the uncertainty of the wireless channel, in this work we consider that the wireless bandwidth follows Rayleigh fading [43]. Since there is no complete information at the MVNO, we need to introduce an outage probability constraint in (19) as

